ial and unique.<br>
<br>
These bags are NOT a part of the plan.  They are an oversight.  It's verants' fault but it's still an oversight.  These bags were meant to be something that rewarded people for their efforts in the tradeskills.  Now, thanks to greed, that accomplishment seems yet again cheapened.<br>
<br>
I also gave as many bags away for free as I could.  Why?  Well it's simple.  I know almost every person on this server capable of actually making on of those trophies, and I'm fairly confident that none of them would ever try to sell those bags for profit.<br>
<br>
My two cents..<br>
